name: Van Gogh + Artaud + Spinetta =
description:
Rencontre entre Van Gogh, Antonin Artaud et Luis Alberto Spinetta.

"Le pont de l'Anglois" Van Gogh, 1888.

"Thus it wormed its way into his body,
This society,
absolved,
consecrated,
sanctified
And possessed,
Erased in him the supernatural consciousness he had just achieved, and like an inundation of black crows in the fibers of his internal tree,
Overwhelmed him with one final surge,
And taking his place,
Killed him."
Artaud, Le suicidé de la société, 1947.

"Cantata de puentes amarillos" Luis Alberto Spinetta


2835 × 2835
